headline: 2 Under-the-Radar REITs With Market-Beating Potential
summary: The real estate sector is off to a strong start in 2025, outperforming the S&P 500 (SNPINDEX: ^GSPC) by about 6 percentage points through mid-March.  Ryman Hospitality Properties (NYSE: RHP) is a hospitality REIT with two main components to its business.  Ryman owns the five massive Gaylord hotels and one other group-focused hotel property.
